{"tid":1115221,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人以為兔子冇感情無視主人, 其實完全相反......","createTime":"2019-04-19T04:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T09:45:40.000Z","uid":197098,"like":35,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e2957482e5157bac363987d5186618b52016e9","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n無視主人的誤會而被棄養：其實兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。所以佢地唔係無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n以下2個videos可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=cec888f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=91447d7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兔子的行為解釋網站：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協: <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=441f905b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站): <a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=49b1142f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂): <a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=91e2aa96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"135d1060cbc72dc026315da39e2cb55c4ec4225e","tid":1115221,"uid":145277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"片2隻兔仔跳得好似狗"},{"pid":"89d3cfbd9110d094d5f8999a7b1290fd3006bac3","tid":1115221,"uid":5891,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"假如我唔知道兔仔會食返自己啲屎嘅話，我都會覺得片1佢係咁舔佢主人係好可愛<br />\n但自從我知道咗之後&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ca0481d9d9d2ffd38c1ed2685cbac670092555","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"89d3cfbd9110d094d5f8999a7b1290fd3006bac3","tid":1115221,"uid":5891,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"假如我唔知道兔仔會食返自己啲屎嘅話，我都會覺得片1佢係咁舔佢主人係好可愛<br />\n但自從我知道咗之後&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"有2種吾同既糞：大多數是正常糞, 硬的(不會吃)<br />\n                             少量是營養糞 (會吃)"},{"pid":"752e7bf258254adffce1ba0b64711068447ddb1d","tid":1115221,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4035d7ce8fe5ba81e53b7ed698ecd21081d6ebf0","tid":1115221,"uid":92042,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"b1ca0481d9d9d2ffd38c1ed2685cbac670092555","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"89d3cfbd9110d094d5f8999a7b1290fd3006bac3","tid":1115221,"uid":5891,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"假如我唔知道兔仔會食返自己啲屎嘅話，我都會覺得片1佢係咁舔佢主人係好可愛<br />\n但自從我知道咗之後&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:03:07.000Z","msg