lyTime":"2019-04-19T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9517eed3dfbec3061d6c1d3b2c9b85e6f29e59b","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d572fd3fc5aac3eef3aa6e72685ef56822e69fa6","tid":1115221,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e32d452318c1b5c7b3bb3d5c4f564a08780fc52","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d572fd3fc5aac3eef3aa6e72685ef56822e69fa6","tid":1115221,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:24:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:51:44.000Z","msg":"是牠們最開心的時候才會跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7138b29def0e86a3cd3c92c8cc82c0dc624d2106","tid":1115221,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T12:54:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b79941231e52da5c94402fb0d64a84638c9592ee","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a03e3b74a271df484ba5b34cddd3fa42fb74088","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T14:48:05.000Z","msg":"兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predator)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的，狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2HMWjTXFwuY&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=c0ea694b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY</a>"},{"pid":"d1e15f2cd6dbcac22a24641770f1806a1292a0bd","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:30:52.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=a247f66e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"},{"pid":"db0b0b10339dcbbf397f52525f9d658ca2d84a43","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):<br />\n<br />\n所有蔬菜要洗乾淨後生食。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每天怎樣餵BB和青少年(7星期-7個月大):</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 1/3 Alfalfa Hay, 2/3 Timothy Hay, 可以加Orchard Hay, Oat Hay 或其他Hay令到更多元化和好味道，任你喜歡:loveliness:<br />\n- 2湯匙-無限兔糧：推介Burgess或Oxbow幼兔糧，其他牌子也可以<br />\n- 12個星期大或以上: 開始給吃1-3條手指長的蔬菜 (要徹底清洗)<br />\n<br />\n<em>注意：</em>24小時無限兔糧是沒問題，但如果牠只吃糧不吃乾草就要減少兔糧，因為消化系統還在生長中，乾草是最重要。喝煲過的冷水，不要給自來水和礦泉水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">怎樣餵年輕成人(7個月-1歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 減少Alfalfa Hay, 增加Timothy Hay和其他Hay<br />\n- 減少到每6磅(兔子體重)半杯兔糧<br />\n- 漸漸地增加蔬菜<br />\n- 極少水果: 每6磅(兔子體重)1-2安士<br />\n<br />\n<em>注意：</em>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">餵成熟成人(1-5歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草：移除Alfalfa Hay, 只供Timothy Hay, Orchard Hay, Oat Hay等等<br />\n- 每6磅1/4-1/2杯糧 / 每5磅1/4杯糧<br />\n- 每6磅最少2杯切好的蔬菜<br />\n- 每6磅2安士或以下(2湯匙)水果/每2磅1茶匙(teaspoon)水果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老兔(6歲以上)：</span><br />\n- 如果兔子能夠維持足夠體重，可以繼續供給以上的食法<br />\n- 年老和身體虛弱的需要增加兔糧，體重過輕的可以給吃Alfalfa Hay(前提是體內鈣質正常)。老兔最好定期去驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我餵很少糧或不餵糧，怎樣補充營養？</span><br />\n- 需要增加蔬菜份量來補充營養 (而卡路里是不需要補充的)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>更多資訊</strong>：<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/faq-diet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Ffaq-diet%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=3f07451d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/faq-diet/</a> <br />\n                   <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/suggested-vegetables-and-fruits-for-a-rabbit-diet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fsuggested-vegetables-and-fruits-for-a-rabbit-diet%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=e3286df6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/suggested-vegetables-and-fruits-for-a-rabbit-diet/</a>"},{"pid":"5590415ddc1ffa15f493d254fb8e11cc4547453d","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c05fce28428d4934208c54a17f8b6564963a91d8","tid":1115221,"uid":133340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89d3cfbd9110d094d5f8999a7b1290fd3006bac3","tid":1115221,"uid":5891,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"假如我唔知道兔仔會食返自己啲屎嘅話，我都會覺得片1佢係咁舔佢主人係好可愛<br />\n但自從我知道咗之後&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"好多動物都會<br />\n反而覺得兔屎感覺良好啲 一粒粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"Rabbits produce two types of droppings: fecal pellets and cecal pellets (aka cecotropes). The former are the dry round ones you usually see in the litterbox, the latter are edible for rabbits which contain essential nutrients."},{"pid":"7d8aabbba0002066be333f166ae45c654627ff91","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca5d6f3894e415ef3f7286ac7ee1e61ebee98f8","tid":1115221,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T09:45:40.000Z","msg":"當兔子🐰受驚時，groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們是很重要，讓牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !"}]}